videos.description: Shaqquan Aaron dribbles into the lane and drops in a left-handed runner before the buzzer.
videos.headline: USC's Aaron hits floater before buzzer

videos.description: Stephen Thompson Jr. delivers a nice pass to Drew Eubanks for a one-handed dunk.
videos.headline: OSU's Banks slips the defense for dunk

videos.description: Chimezie Metu blocks Alfred Hollins' shot and runs over to send Seth Berger's putback attempt into the stands.
videos.headline: USC's Metu denies access to rim twice

videos.description: Jonah Mathews runs the break and dumps it off to Nick Rakocevic for a two-handed flush.
videos.headline: USC's Rakocevic beats everyone for fast-break dunk

videos.description: Jordan McLaughlin steals the pass and delivers a lob to Chimezie Metu for an alley-oop dunk.
videos.headline: USC's McLaughlin steals and deals for alley-oop
